2. `plugins.code_safety` - coze-openclaw-plugin 代码审查\n3. `plugins.code_safety` - wecom-openclaw-plugin 代码审查\n\n**建议**: 配置 `gateway.auth` token 加强安全\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 结论\n\n**✅ 全部功能验证通过！v5.0.0 已就绪发布！**\n\n所有新增功能在当前环境下运行正常，可以安全使用 🍀"],"finalPromptText":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50a10a0730a4b3cbe46c9cab374\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-05 10:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50a10a0730a4b3cbe46c9cab374]\nhaidong: 在当前环境下验证一下刚刚升级的全部功能，实际执行一下。","itemLifecycle":{"startedCount":31,"completedCount":31,"activeCount":0},"toolMetas":[{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → print text → print text → run bash scripts/quick-check.sh (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"========================================\" && echo \"🔥 验证1: …`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → print text → print text → print text → run python3 agent/quick-check-agent.py (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"\" && echo \"========================================\" && ech…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → print text → print text → print text → run python3 agent/realtime-monitor.py (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"\" && echo \"========================================\" && ech…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → print text → print text → print text → print text -> show first 80 lines (+1 steps) (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd 